Name: Whiskey
Description: A distilled alcoholic beverage made from fermented grain mash.

Name: Vodka
Description: A clear and colorless distilled spirit, typically made from fermented grains or potatoes.

Name: Rum
Description: A distilled alcoholic beverage made from sugarcane byproducts, such as molasses or sugarcane juice.

Name: Beer
Description: A fermented alcoholic beverage made from cereal grains, hops, water, and yeast.

Name: Wine
Description: An alcoholic beverage made from fermented grapes or other fruits.

Name: Tequila
Description: A distilled spirit made from the blue agave plant, primarily produced in the Tequila region of Mexico.

Name: Gin
Description: A clear distilled spirit made with juniper berries and various botanicals.
